headline: Fastenal Company Announces Cash Dividend
summary: WINONA, Minn., October 10, 2025--Fastenal Company (Nasdaq:FAST) ('Fastenal,' 'we,' 'our,' or 'us') reported its board of directors declared a dividend of $0.22 per share to be paid in cash on November 25, 2025 to shareholders of record at the close of business on October 28, 2025.
